# <type>(<scope>): <subject>
#
# Types:
#   feat, fix, refactor, perf, test, docs, build, ci, chore, revert
#
# Scope examples:
#   order, user, system, application, domain, infrastructure,
#   interfaces, shared, readme, docker, swagger, bruno, migration
#
# Good examples:
#   feat(order): add idempotency key support
#   fix(user): handle duplicate email conflict
#   refactor(application): split order usecase by action
#
# Body (optional):
#   - what changed
#   - why changed
#   - impact/risk
#
# Breaking change:
#   type(scope)!: subject
#   and explain migration steps in body
